    </cit>
    <etym xml:lang="ru">Отложительный падеж от <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><lang/><w>ganzraxad</w><gloss><q>умышленно</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><w/><gloss><q>с умыслом</q></gloss></mentioned>, , которое само
        представляет наречное образование от <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><lang/><w>ganzraxva</w><gloss><q>замышлять</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><w/><gloss><q>замысел</q></gloss></mentioned>, ; такое же наращение
        осетинского наречного форманта на грузинский имеем в %inardwatæj%i ‘в подряд’, ‘сдельно’
        (см. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_nardwat"/>). Смещение значения ‘замысел’ → ‘измена’
        произошло, возможно, под влиянием таких грузинских выражений, как <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                ><lang/><w>ganzraxva ǧalatʼisa</w><gloss><q>замышлять
        измену</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">Ablative case from <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><lang/><w>ganzraxad</w><gloss><q>deliberately</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><w/><gloss><q>intentionally</q></gloss></mentioned>, , which is in its
        turn an adverbial derivative from <mentioned xml:lang="ka"
                    ><lang/><w>ganzraxva</w><gloss><q>conceive</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><w/><gloss><q>conception</q></gloss></mentioned>, ; the same augmentation
        of Ossetic adverbial formant on a Georgian word is presented in %inardwatæj%i ‘by the job’
        (see <ref type="xr" target="#entry_nardwat"/>). The change of the meaning ‘conception’ →
        ‘treason’ might have probably occured, influenced by Georgian expressions such as <mentioned
            xml:lang="ka"><lang/><w>ganzraxva ǧalatʼisa</w><gloss><q>plan
            treason</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
</entry>
